node.text:
✨🍎GIVEAWAY🍎✨SO MANY of you told us how much you love @thatsit bars that we decided to GIVEAWAY $1,000 TO #WALMART!!! We hope to help a family in a BIG WAY and celebrate #Thatsit fruit bars being available nationwide at @walmart ALSO 5 additional winners will get a year supply of @thatsit fruit snacks! 🎉

All you have to do to enter is:
✨Follow @thatsit + @taytumandoakley
✨Like and Save this post
✨Tag your snack besties (1 tag = 1 entry)
BONUS ENTRY: Drop a "🍎” on our last three posts 

Giveaway open to USA only. Closes September 13th at 11:59pm PT. Good luck!

Winner will be contacted via DM directly from @thatsit. We will never ask you to verify winnings or for personal information outside of the app. @thatsit & @taytumandoakley are the only accounts associated with this giveaway. Winners will have 48 hours to respond @thatsit to claim prize. #ThatsIt #ThatsItPartner
